title: ng-conf
description:
ng-conf 2024 is a two-day double track conference focused on building the Angular community. AG Grid has been a platinum sponsor of ng-conf for a number of years and will be a platinum sponsor once again in 2024. 

In addition one of our senior engineers, Stephen Cooper, will be giving a talk titled: 'Perfecting your Profiling Skills' which will show how you can use Angular Dev Tools alongside the standard Dev Tools to identify and resolve performance issues, whilst unearthing some hidden gems in the process.

title: React Summit
description: React Summit is an annual conference on all things React, gathering thousands of Front-end and Full-stack engineers from around the world.
